o To build with GNU:
  % env LIBS="-lstdc++" CXXFLAGS="-O3 -mavx2 -g -fkeep-inline-functions" ./configure
  % env LIBS="-lstdc++" CXXFLAGS="-fkeep-inline-functions" ./configure --enable-debug --disable-shared

o To build with Intel:
  % env CXX=icpc CC=icc FC=ifort LIBS="-lstdc++" CXXFLAGS="-fPIC -m64 -g -O3 -fkeep-inline-functions" ./configure
